And I am american
And I have a personal account with
| Field    | Value           |
| Absence  | Vacation |
| FromDate | 2014-01-01      |
| Accrued  | 25              |
And I have an absence with
| Field     | Value            |
| Name      | Vacation  |
| StartTime | 2014-01-01 00:00 |
| EndTime   | 2014-01-03 23:59 |
